Wowww yaaar it's so amazing 🥰🥺🎶😌🎶
I love string instruments a lot. And in this also they used India traditional string instruments. I liked it so much.
They started off the song like acapella. And in the middle, jugalbandhi type with that tic tic (sorry IDK what it's name 😅) instruments. Those are the best. I loved how they blended traditional and modern instruments together. And singing also awesome. 
I truly loved it 😍🥰
